    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>the main purpose of this class is to avoid copy and move constructor and assignment operator implementation in <ref refid="classMR_1_1Object" kindref="compound">Object</ref> class, which has too many fields for that; since every object stores a pointer on its parent, copying of this object does not copy the children and moving is taken with care </para>
